{"actor":"Ryan Snodgrass","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T12:11:26Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":104,"issue_id":"ox-ok3","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"ox-ok3\",\"title\":\"Fix concurrent agent recording race condition\",\"description\":\"Ghost-clearing logic in StartRecording, runAgentSessionStart, and startSessionRecording treats recordings from different agent IDs as ghosts and deletes them, destroying active recordings from concurrent agents sharing the same XDG cache (same repo ID). Fix: add agent-aware recording state functions and update all agent-context callers.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"owner\":\"ryan@sageox.ai\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-05T20:11:21Z\",\"created_by\":\"Ryan Snodgrass\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-05T20:11:21Z\"}"}
{"actor":"Ryan Snodgrass","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T12:20:57Z","event_type":"closed","id":105,"issue_id":"ox-ok3","new_value":"Implemented: 5 agent-aware functions in recording.go, fixed all agent-context callers across 11 files, added 4 concurrent agent regression tests. All 5761 tests pass, 0 lint issues.","old_value":""}
{"actor":"Ryan Snodgrass","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T14:54:17Z","event_type":"created","id":106,"issue_id":"ox-n6f","new_value":"","old_value":""}
{"actor":"Ryan Snodgrass","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T15:14:16Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":107,"issue_id":"ox-n6f","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"ox-n6f\",\"title\":\"Fix stale file paths in session stop output after ledger upload\",\"description\":\"After successful ledger upload, ox agent session stop prunes the local cache (os.RemoveAll) but returns JSON output with raw_path, events_path, html_path, summary_md_path, session_md_path still pointing to the deleted cache directory. The summary_prompt (built before pruning) also embeds the stale cache path. This causes agents to search for non-existent files and incorrectly conclude 'the session recording file wasn't written to disk.' Observed in test-public repo where a valid session with entries was processed and uploaded successfully, but the agent couldn't find the files afterward.\\n\\nTwo fixes needed:\\n\\n1. CLI (cmd/ox/agent_session.go ~line 947): After successful cache pruning, clear stale paths in result (RawPath, EventsPath, HTMLPath, SummaryMDPath, SessionMDPath, PlanPath) or replace them with ledger paths.\\n\\n2. summary_prompt path: BuildSummaryPrompt is called at line 838 (before upload/pruning) and embeds result.RawPath. Either rebuild the prompt after upload with the ledger path, or ensure the prompt uses ledger_session_dir when available. The skill (extensions/claude/commands/ox-session-stop.md lines 14-15) instructs agents to read from the path in summary_prompt, which is stale.\\n\\nKey files:\\n- cmd/ox/agent_session.go (processAgentSession, ~lines 838-950)\\n- internal/session/summarize.go (BuildSummaryPrompt)\\n- extensions/claude/commands/ox-session-stop.md\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"owner\":\"ryan@sageox.ai\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-05T22:54:17Z\",\"created_by\":\"Ryan Snodgrass\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-05T22:54:17Z\"}"}
{"actor":"Ryan Snodgrass","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T15:15:11Z","event_type":"closed","id":108,"issue_id":"ox-n6f","new_value":"Fixed: after cache prune, rewrite result paths to ledger equivalents and rebuild summary prompt","old_value":""}
