{"actor":"Ryan Snodgrass","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T15:27:22Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":110,"issue_id":"ox-ra2","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"ox-ra2\",\"title\":\"Add LFS pointer file I/O to internal/lfs\",\"description\":\"Complete the internal git-lfs implementation by adding WritePointerFile(s), IsPointerFile, ReadPointerFile to pointer.go. Update WriteSessionMeta to auto-create pointer files. Update CheckHydrationStatus to use IsPointerFile. Update commit functions to stage pointer files. Refactor import.go to use WritePointerFiles.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"feature\",\"owner\":\"ryan@sageox.ai\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-05T23:27:20Z\",\"created_by\":\"Ryan Snodgrass\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-05T23:27:20Z\"}"}
