{"actor":"Ryan Snodgrass","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-06T10:45:14Z","event_type":"updated","id":125,"issue_id":"ox-xi5","new_value":"{\"description\":\"New subcommand to add an expert coworker to a team's context repo. Usage: ox coworker add \\u003cfilename\\u003e [--team \\u003cid\\u003e]. Workflow: (1) Validate .md file has YAML frontmatter with required 'description' field, warn if 'model' missing. (2) Resolve target team path via FindRepoTeamContext or --team flag. (3) Copy to \\u003cteam_path\\u003e/coworkers/agents/\\u003cname\\u003e.md. (4) git add + git commit in the team context repo. Daemon handles push on next sync cycle. Users can also manually git commit coworker files — this command is a convenience wrapper with validation.\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"ox-xi5\",\"title\":\"Add ox coworker add \\u003cfilename\\u003e command\",\"description\":\"New subcommand to add an expert coworker to a team. Usage: ox coworker add reviewer.md [--team \\u003cid\\u003e]. Validates .md frontmatter (description, optional model), resolves target team path via FindRepoTeamContext or --team flag, copies to \\u003cteam_path\\u003e/coworkers/agents/\\u003cname\\u003e.md, confirms success.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"feature\",\"owner\":\"ryan@sageox.ai\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T18:40:04Z\",\"created_by\":\"Ryan Snodgrass\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T18:40:04Z\"}"}
{"actor":"Ryan Snodgrass","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-06T10:45:15Z","event_type":"updated","id":126,"issue_id":"ox-8mx","new_value":"{\"description\":\"New subcommand to remove an expert coworker from a team's context repo. Usage: ox coworker remove \\u003cname\\u003e [--team \\u003cid\\u003e] [--force]. Takes coworker name (not filename). Prompts for confirmation unless --force. Deletes \\u003cteam_path\\u003e/coworkers/agents/\\u003cname\\u003e.md, then git add + git commit the deletion in the team context repo. Daemon handles push on next sync cycle.\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"ox-8mx\",\"title\":\"Add ox coworker remove \\u003cname\\u003e command\",\"description\":\"New subcommand to remove an expert coworker from a team. Usage: ox coworker remove \\u003cname\\u003e [--team \\u003cid\\u003e] [--force]. Takes coworker name (not filename). Prompts for confirmation unless --force. Deletes \\u003cteam_path\\u003e/coworkers/agents/\\u003cname\\u003e.md.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"feature\",\"owner\":\"ryan@sageox.ai\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T18:40:05Z\",\"created_by\":\"Ryan Snodgrass\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-06T18:40:05Z\"}"}
